# SHL GenAI RAG Tool 🔍

This project is built for SHL's Generative AI Assessment. It recommends the most relevant SHL assessments based on a user’s input of job descriptions or roles using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔎 Search for SHL assessments using natural language queries
- 📊 Returns top recommended assessments based on similarity
- ✅ Displays metadata: duration, support type, test type, and adaptive format
- 🧠 Uses embeddings and cosine similarity for retrieval

